Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomomi, where did you put my bead bracelet?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You better! Why you cleaned up my room?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}'Cause, it was a mess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it wasn't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You seriously didn't see the bead bracelet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I didn't. Besides, when did you buy that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you remember it? It has little bell on it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't remember.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty old picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bracelet. Don't you remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, was it really in your room before I cleaned it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you left it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, let's use the final way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What final way? What are you up to, Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can teleport to the bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I look everywhere and it's nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we end up somewhere other than your room, get ready for consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this's a big room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird. Why did we end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you weren't concentrating, Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then is the bracelet here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how come we ended up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little girl took away my bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fast runner, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tickle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it was your bracelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did she have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't they chop down that zelkova tree years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, gotta find the girl first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to tell me what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, watch out for the cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go? Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't changed since we were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't eaten snacks. Besides we were running all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a bit hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we running around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how come your bracelet was there? Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you, Mikage-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy got us this. Tomomi-chan's got the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My daddy brings us just cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have good daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found crepe shop! I'll have chocolate banana! What's wrong, Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's got chocolate banana!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant, my bracelet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Mikage-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling you. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she? A monkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so heavy. Go on diet, Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? I should be slimmer than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we'll teleport to the bracelet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I preferred the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK, obachan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, obachan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are. Did the ball hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're OK, boys. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see a girl? She runs real fast and has yellow bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, you two. Let's go, Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, obachan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, pregnant dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those stupid brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. It's only an innocent trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How innocent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kind of kids wouldn't do any good even when they grow up. I know they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, sure. But one of them was really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got real bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I? Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should we trust those stupid brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, they called me obachan. They gotta be blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way did she go? Gotta find her or it'll get dark soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, do you see her that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I was reading book, so I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. It's my fault. You're very good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to seeing you in ten years. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, did you come from that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see a girl with yellow bracelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was reading book, so I'm not too sure, but I think a girl making a bell sound went by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mobile kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead end?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She crossed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gotta be ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't loose to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tomomi, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to swing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can let you if you can lend me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No bracelet, no swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have my daddy's restaurant's free smorgasbord ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll throw in the special dinner show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what? I'll tell her to give it back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But looks like she really likes it. It's too cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you can't run! Now, lend me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, did you see that? She could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage! Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's broken. It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bracelet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mikage! Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't wanna go after the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There. You can have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's your's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile, Tomomi, Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:21:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I gave my bracelet to Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Thanks. I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go find the bracelet together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, what do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, how can you make this much mess just trying to find the bracelet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHUDDUP!! You clean up the mess by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, where did you go in midnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was playing with the unicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unicorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, let's fly to London in dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls,\N"Unicorn under Moonlight."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.22,0:22:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai, I'll see you in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:08.26,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:11.56,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:14.89,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:18.10,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:34.75,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:38.04,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,, that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:51.55,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know it better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:57.98,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:05.03,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:11.78,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:14.70,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:20.12,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:23.17,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.63,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:29.72,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:33.10,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,are better than one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:24.61,credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ending Song\N"There has to be Both of Us"\N("Futarijanakya Dame Nano")\NBy Dio
